  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients who received antibiotics for presumed infection

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Prolonged therapy (eg, endocarditis)

          -  Severe immunosuppression

          -  Severe infections (due to viruses, parasites, or Mycobacterium tuberculosis)

          -  Patients previously infected or colonized with multidrug resistant pathogens and
             moribund patients.
      </textblock>
